ed="T" n="0802c17"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0802c17"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date>吳郡包山<persName key="A011078">神皓</persName>傳（<persName key="A011089">維亮</persName>）</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0802c18"/><persName key="A011078">釋神皓</persName>，字<persName key="A011078">恒度</persName><ptr target="#n472"/>，姓<name>徐</name>氏。八代祖<persName key="A005886">摛</persName>，齊竟陵王<lb
ed="T" n="0802c19"/>西邸學士。子<persName key="A004803">陵</persName>，梁尚書左僕射，其文與<persName key="A005005"><anchor xml:id="beg0802005"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>庚</sic><corr>庾</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0802005"/><lb
ed="T" n="0802c20"/>子山</persName>齊名，迨陳國亡，因佐<placeName key="PL000000009913">吳邑</placeName>，遂家<placeName key="PL000000009928">姑<lb
ed="T" n="0802c21"/>蘇</placeName>。<persName key="A011078">皓</persName>乃為<placeName key="PL000000009928">吳郡</placeName>人也。天性耿潔，風韻朗邁。<lb
ed="T" n="0802c22"/>幼負脫俗之姿，尋依錢塘<placeName key="PL000000011482">龍泉道場</placeName><persName key="A004177">一公</persName>出<lb
ed="T" n="0802c23"/>家。<date from-iso="+0747-02-18" key="j19939441994298" to-iso="+0748-02-07"><name>天寶</name>六年</date>，降版詔精擇真行，一州許<lb
ed="T" n="0802c24"/>度三人，<persName key="A011078">皓</persName>居薦首，因隷僧籍于<placeName key="PL000000010052">包山</placeName><placeName key="PL000000010073">福願<lb
ed="T" n="0802c25"/>道場</placeName>。初進具於<persName key="A011085">興大師</persName>，次通《律鈔》於<persName key="A004177">曇一</persName>。<lb
ed="T" n="0802c26"/>後<choice resp="sgsz"><sic>士</sic><corr>十</corr></choice>講<ptr target="#n473"/>《律鈔》，五昇壇場。遂乘舟歸<placeName key="PL000000010052">包山</placeName>，使<lb
ed="T" n="0802c27"/>野叟誅茅，山童掃石，逍遙棲息。旋增修屋<lb
ed="T" n="0802c28"/>宇。<date from-iso="+0758-03-22" key="j19979941998315" to-iso="+0759-02-06"><name>乾元</name>元祀</date>，有詔天下二十七寺，各奏大德<lb
ed="T" n="0802c29"/>七人，長講戒律。因請住開元寺<!--找不到此地-->，欲果其願，<pb ed="T" n="0803a" xml:id="T50.2061.0803a"/><lb
ed="T" n="0803a01"/>且懼簡書，遂僶俛從命。奉戒弟子<placeName key="PL000000034453">開州</placeName>刺史<lb
ed="T" n="0803a02"/><persName key="A011086">陸向前</persName>、給事中<persName key="A019378">嚴<g ref="#Z1239"/></persName>、服道弟子禮部侍郎<persName key="A011087">劉太<lb
ed="T" n="0803a03"/>真</persName>、前大理評事<persName key="A011088">張象</persName>、欽風弟子前廉<anchor xml:id="beg0803sgsz1"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>史</sic><corr>使</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0803sgsz1"/>亞相<persName key="A011011">李<lb
ed="T" n="0803a04"/>棲筠</persName>請綱任海隅。一邑緇伍，三變至于道。<lb
ed="T" n="0803a05"/><date from-iso="+0759-11-21" key="j19986031998806" to-iso="+0760-06-11">末年</date>工於圓宗，別置西方法社，誦《法華經》<lb
ed="T" n="0803a06"/>九千餘部。<date from-iso="+0790-11-15" key="j20099202009949" to-iso="+0790-12-14"><name>貞元</name>六年十月</date>開元寺<!--找不到此地-->遇疾，至<date from-iso="+0581-02-22" key="j19333191936714" to-iso="+0590-06-10">十<lb
ed="T" n="0803a07"/>二月</date>，顧囑弟子<persName key="A011089">維亮</persName><ptr target="#n477"/>曰：「<persName key="A011078">我</persName>棄世後，可歸<placeName key="PL000000010052">洞<lb
ed="T" n="0803a08"/>庭故山</placeName>置塔。」說法而終。是夜瑠璃<anchor xml:id="beg0803sgsz3"/>色<anchor xml:id="end0803sgsz3"/>天，星<lb
ed="T" n="0803a09"/>霣如雨，西方兆眹，密現于前。春秋七十五，<lb
ed="T" n="0803a10"/>僧臘四十三。門人<persName key="A011089">維亮</persName>有文有道，獨步當<lb
ed="T" n="0803a11"/>時，執師之喪，不以證而廢教也。傳法弟子<lb
ed="T" n="0803a12"/><persName key="A011090">道超</persName>、<persName key="A011092">靈俊</persName>、<persName key="A011093">道濬</persName>、<persName key="A011094">道稜</persName>、<persName key="A011095">維讓</persName>、<persName key="A011096">維誠</persName>，皆一時英邁。<lb
ed="T" n="0803a13"/><placeName key="PL000000013012">霅</placeName><persName key="A008833">晝</persName>為墳塔碑頌美云。</p>
